creator: Alex Solutions
descriptionHtml:
Completely FREE workout app provides you the possibility to workout at home or in the gym and track your performance. Easily share your workout routine with your friends! Make your progress more visible to your friends or a coach. Engage with your friends by achieving the best exercise results.

The app has exercises for all main muscles and the possibility to workout offline.

Features:
- useful statistic in tables and graphics
- extensive statistics by exercises, programs, personal weight
- timer feature shows the rest time between attempts
- saved result from the previous exercise to help you choose a correct workout strategy
- convenient weight builder for barbell
- effective time trackers for all types of activities
- functionality that allows to add custom exercise
- ability to create a new program based on finished workout
- sharing programs with friends
- tracking a friend's progress
- friend's best result statistics


This free sport and fitness app is your great tool for losing weight or gaining muscles.
You can create a bodybuilding workout plan that will help prepare your body for perfect shape. Together with a barbell constructor, the strength training can be much easier.
Custom-build timer can be used for a fat-burning workout, stretching and static exercises.
HIIT workout can be easily performed with help of a timer rest mode between training.
Gym static provides a list of exercises for training at home even without equipment.
A fitness coach can track your progress using “Friend” functionality to provide a better program.
